{%- comment -%}
  bd a7av.12 / a7av.24 — Quick Buy (native STKY replacement).

  J11 S13 redesign (web-team, 2026-06-11): the overlay ADD TO CART bar is replaced
  by the STKY-style round cart+plus icon at the UPPER-RIGHT of the product image
  (bg #E4E5E6 @ 50%, always visible — no hover gating).
  - Single-variant: tapping the icon adds via the shared [data-vrec-add] AJAX
    handler (assets/hairmnl-common.js → /cart/add.js → opens the drawer).
  - Multi-variant: tapping opens a variant-selector popover (variant + price
    rows); tapping a row adds that variant. Popover JS in hairmnl-common.js
    ([data-qb-toggle], click-outside closes).
  - Sold out: no icon (the card already communicates sold-out state).

  Renders on ALL product-card surfaces (grids + every rec rail) — June 10/11
  web-team direction. Anchored by a position:relative wrapper in the card
  (.product-grid-item__media / .vrec-card__media); CSS in css-overrides.liquid.

  Arg: product {Product} required.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if product != blank -%}
  {%- assign qb_variant = product.first_available_variant -%}
  {%- if qb_variant and product.available -%}
    {%- comment -%} J16 S13 (bd a7av.26): bolder + larger cart-plus glyph — the team
        found the previous thin/small vector "faded". stroke-width 2, solid currentColor;
        the #E4E5E6@50% circle bg stays per the J11 spec (sizing bumped in css-overrides). {%- endcomment -%}
    {%- capture qb_icon_svg -%}
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
        <path d="M1.6 3.4h2.3l1.95 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.47 1.2h6.7a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.46-1.15L17 6.7H5.1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        <circle cx="8.2" cy="19.1" r="1.55" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="14.7" cy="19.1" r="1.55" fill="currentColor"/>
        <path d="M19.6 2.9v5.2M17 5.5h5.2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
    {%- endcapture -%}
    <div class="quick-buy" data-quick-buy>
      {%- if product.variants.size > 1 -%}
        <button type="button"
                class="quick-buy__icon"
                data-qb-toggle
                aria-haspopup="true"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-label="{{ 'products.product.add_to_cart' | t | default: 'Add to cart' }}: {{ product.title | strip_html | escape }}">
          {{ qb_icon_svg }}
        </button>
        <div class="quick-buy__popover" data-qb-popover>
          {%- for v in product.variants -%}
            <button type="button"
                    class="quick-buy__option"
                    {% if v.available %}data-vrec-add data-variant-id="{{ v.id }}"{% else %}disabled aria-disabled="true"{% endif %}>
              <span class="quick-buy__option-title">{{ v.title }}</span>
              <span class="quick-buy__option-price">{% if v.available %}{{ v.price | money }}{% else %}{{ 'products.product.sold_out' | t | default: 'Sold out' }}{% endif %}</span>
            </button>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      {%- else -%}
        <button type="button"
                class="quick-buy__icon"
                data-vrec-add
                data-variant-id="{{ qb_variant.id }}"
                aria-label="{{ 'products.product.add_to_cart' | t | default: 'Add to cart' }}: {{ product.title | strip_html | escape }}">
          {{ qb_icon_svg }}
        </button>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
